I am cold.&nbsp;

Want warm arms around me. Now.

Some serious visualization in order.

I was wondering why there were policemen on the underground yesterday... There's a concrete threat of a terrorist attack.&nbsp; 

Not really good news when you live 15 minutes walk from the centre and there are 2 possible targets just 10 minutes walk down the road :-( 

The sightseeing plan for today should better be canceled I guess... Hmph.&nbsp;
